# PM2 Korumasi

## Calisan servisler (VDS snapshot)

| id | name | status |
|----|------|--------|
| 0 | `owlhuntbot-shard` | online |
| 1 | `owlhuntbot-worker` | online |

`pm2 list` ile guncel durumu dogrula; tablo degismisse kullaniciya bildir.

## Kurallar

- PM2 sureclerini **otomatik restart etme** (`pm2 restart`, `pm2 reload`, `pm2 stop`, `pm2 delete`, `pm2 kill`).
- Asla calistirma: `pm2 delete all`, `pm2 kill`.
- Restart gerekirse komutu goster ve **onay bekle**:

```bash
pm2 restart owlhuntbot-shard owlhuntbot-worker
# veya tek process:
pm2 restart owlhuntbot-shard
```

- `pm2 logs`, `pm2 status`, `pm2 list`, `pm2 describe` — okuma icin serbest.
